title: $:/plugins/rimir/cascade-palette/search-meta/name
tags: $:/tags/rimir/cascade-palette/search-meta
ca-meta-key: name
ca-chip: 🏷 Name
ca-hint: Match against the row's displayed label.
ca-help: When pushed, the matcher reads each row's DISPLAYED label — the active name-lens / row-label projection (e.g. the `caption` from the shipped "Caption → Title" lens), exactly what you see in the list — so the match always highlights in place on the label. This is the default search slot when no Meta pill is pushed at all. Combine with other Meta pills (e.g. Hint) to widen the slot set per row. To match the raw tiddler title instead of the displayed label, push the Title field pill.
ca-order: 100
